---
// Timeline.astro - Alternating timeline component
---

<section  class="py-16 px-4 bg-white">
    <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto">
      <h2 class="text-2xl font-normal mb-4 text-left">Historia</h2>
      <hr class="pt-2 pb-6 border-t border-gray-200" />


  
      <!-- Alternating Content Blocks -->
    <div class="space-y-12">
      <!-- Block 1 - Left -->
      <div data-aos="zoom-in-right" class="flex flex-col md:flex-row gap-8 items-center">
        <div class="w-full md:w-1/2">
          <div class="bg-gray-50 p-6 md:p-8 rounded-lg shadow-sm h-full">
            <img 
              src="/placeholder.svg?height=200&width=400" 
              alt="International Shipping" 
              class="w-full h-48 object-cover rounded-lg mb-6"
            />
            <h3 class="text-xl font-bold mb-3 text-gray-900">International Shipping</h3>
            <p class="text-gray-600">
              We provide reliable international shipping services to ensure your goods arrive safely and on time. 
              Our extensive network of carriers allows us to offer competitive rates and flexible delivery options 
              to meet your specific needs.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="w-full md:w-1/2 hidden md:block"></div>
      </div>
      
      <!-- Block 2 - Right -->
      <div data-aos="zoom-in-left" class="flex flex-col md:flex-row gap-8 items-center">
        <div class="w-full md:w-1/2 hidden md:block"></div>
        <div class="w-full md:w-1/2">
          <div class="bg-gray-50 p-6 md:p-8 rounded-lg shadow-sm h-full">
            <img 
              src="/placeholder.svg?height=200&width=400" 
              alt="Customs Clearance" 
              class="w-full h-48 object-cover rounded-lg mb-6"
            />
            <h3 class="text-xl font-bold mb-3 text-gray-900">Customs Clearance</h3>
            <p class="text-gray-600">
              Navigating customs regulations can be complex. Our experienced team handles all aspects of customs 
              clearance, ensuring your imports comply with local regulations and minimizing delays. We manage 
              documentation, duties, and taxes to streamline the process.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
      
      <!-- Block 3 - Left -->
      <div data-aos="zoom-in-right" class="flex flex-col md:flex-row gap-8 items-center">
        <div class="w-full md:w-1/2">
          <div class="bg-gray-50 p-6 md:p-8 rounded-lg shadow-sm h-full">
            <img 
              src="/placeholder.svg?height=200&width=400" 
              alt="Warehousing Solutions" 
              class="w-full h-48 object-cover rounded-lg mb-6"
            />
            <h3 class="text-xl font-bold mb-3 text-gray-900">Warehousing Solutions</h3>
            <p class="text-gray-600">
              Our secure warehousing facilities offer flexible storage solutions for your imported goods. 
              With inventory management systems and climate-controlled options, we ensure your products 
              are stored safely until they're ready for distribution.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="w-full md:w-1/2 hidden md:block"></div>
      </div>
      
      <!-- Block 4 - Right -->
      <div data-aos="zoom-in-left" class="flex flex-col md:flex-row gap-8 items-center">
        <div class="w-full md:w-1/2 hidden md:block"></div>
        <div class="w-full md:w-1/2">
          <div class="bg-gray-50 p-6 md:p-8 rounded-lg shadow-sm h-full">
            <img 
              src="/placeholder.svg?height=200&width=400" 
              alt="Consulting Services" 
              class="w-full h-48 object-cover rounded-lg mb-6"
            />
            <h3 class="text-xl font-bold mb-3 text-gray-900">Consulting Services</h3>
            <p class="text-gray-600">
              Our import consulting team provides expert guidance on international trade regulations, 
              tariff classifications, and compliance requirements. We help you navigate the complexities 
              of global trade to optimize your import operations and avoid costly mistakes.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
    </div>
  </section>
  
  
  
  

  